Package: meta3l
Title: Three-Level Meta-Analysis via metafor
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Thais", "Author", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a clean, single-call API for conducting three-level meta-analyses
    using the metafor package. Handles multilevel modeling complexity (escalc, vcalc,
    rma.mv, robust variance estimation, and I-squared decomposition) transparently,
    supports multiple effect size measures (proportions, risk ratios, odds ratios,
    standardized mean differences), and produces publication-quality forest plots.
